flowchart TD
    A[Seller fills Create Listing form] --> B{Input validation}
    B -->|Invalid| C[Show 'Please complete required fields']
    C --> A
    B -->|Valid| D[Save listing - status Available]
    D --> E[Show 'Listing posted successfully']
    D --> F[Listings page]
    F --> G[Buyer searches / filters by category and price]
    G --> H[Listing detail view]
    H --> I[Buyer sends contact request - status Pending]
    I --> J{Seller accepts?}
    J -->|Declined| K[Buyer notified - no contact revealed]
    J -->|Accepted| L[Contact details revealed to both sides]
    L --> M[Deal completed on campus]
    M --> N[Seller updates listing status to Sold]
    N --> O[Dashboard recalculates totals by status and category]
    P[Admin reviews listings] --> Q[Update status / remove invalid listing]
    Q --> F
    Q --> O
